Feature: list interactions

  Background: Set the authentication
    Given I authenticate as "user1"
    And I create a "board" with:
      | name | CheckApp |
    And I invite "user2" as member with:
      | type | normal |
    And I create a "list" with:
      | name    | ToReview   |
      | idBoard | {board.id} |

